{"tid":817344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【博紅瀨嘢】着噴血吊帶背心騎馬遊街 性感女咁下場","createTime":"2018-09-13T10:12:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T11:53:01.000Z","uid":150685,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1c907988f49c9a466bfda41ff3b124c01e40f46a","tid":817344,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T10:12:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180913/large/1536769218_57c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180913%2Flarge%2F1536769218_57c3.jpg&h=acff8218&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前日深夜11時許，有內地網民上載影片，畫面中可見一名身穿黑色透視吊帶背心、身材姣好的年輕女子，騎着一匹深啡色的馬，在上海延安路上悠閒散步，沿路一輛輛汽車駛過，馬匹更曾一度跑了起來，吸引不少途人圍觀拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">目擊者在旁問她「你在搞甚麼活動嗎？」女子微笑回答：「沒有啊，就自己養的寵物啊。」又有人問：「這匹馬為甚麼長得那麼強壯？」女子回答：「買的時候就這樣呀。」不過，她最後被被警方截停了。<br />\n<br />\n影片曝光後，引發網民熱議，有人稱：「馬路，當然是馬行的」，亦有人諷刺道：「難道路上不能開寶馬嗎？」</span><br />\n<br />\n上海黃浦公安局通報，女子姓胡，現年26歲，所騎馬匹是從外省市購得，當晚她是為了博取他人關注，從家中將馬匹騎至事發地點，警方已對她作出行政警告處罰，並暫扣馬匹。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180913/large/1536769218_0c08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180913%2Flarge%2F1536769218_0c08.jpg&h=7be2698d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180913/58671934\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180913%2F58671934&d=fKS%2B8ftiISyyt3LDjTGZuJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=d8b98505\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180913%2F58671934&h=2fd30317\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180913/58671934</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條女啲對話"},{"pid":"5f61b9a68a9587d57a4da4d5071ad4c87cae8a7a","ti